Title: An Act Changing the Name of Bago City Elementary School in Bago City, Province of Negros Occidental, to Pang-Ala-Alang Paaralang Heneral Juan A. Araneta
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 238
An Act Changing the Name of Bago City Elementary School in Bago City, Province of Negros Occidental, to Pang-Ala-Alang Paaralang Heneral Juan A. Araneta
Section 1. The name of Bago City Elementary School in Bago City, Province of Negros Occidental, is hereby changed to Pang-alaalang Paaralang Heneral Juan A. Araneta.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: September 12, 1982
